                Root cause analysis
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#0D9488]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                Automatic CAPA linkage
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/contact" class="mt-8 block w-full rounded-lg border border-[#0D9488] px-4 py-2.5 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-[#0D9488] hover:bg-[#0D9488] hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Start Free Trial
