                Certificate management
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#0D9488]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
