          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-[#0D9488]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> Audit trail with hash chain</span>
            <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5"><svg class="h-4 w-4 text-[#0D9488]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg> E-signature approvals</span>
